text: The brown booby is a large and common booby in the family Sulidae. The brown booby eats fish and nests only on the ground. == Appearance == Brown boobys live in most oceans and have yellow or green legs. The brown booby has wings that can grow to about 4 feet. They are normally and are 2.5 feet tall. They have a giant white stomach and a swan shaped head.
title: Brown booby
